entry.title: 关于無铭诚品|About Winmix
entry.content:
深圳市无铭诚品科技有限公司是专业生产加工，开发，销售为一体的公司，是一家专业从事高端定制机械键盘/键帽的生产企业，键帽工艺有浸染、镭雕，热升华、五面热升华等，企业现致力于电商平台和国际业务合作，争取为客户提供更优质的产品以及服务。主营,机械键盘/键帽/拔键器/机械键盘外设加工等。拥有完整、科学的质量管理体系。深圳市无铭诚品科技有限公司的诚信、实力和产品质量获得业界的认可。目前公司在深圳和东莞均有工厂，厂房面积共4500平方米。欢迎各界朋友莅临参观、指导和业务洽谈。
  Shenzhen Wuming Chengpin Technology Co., Ltd. is a company specializing in production, processing, development, designing and sales. It's a professional manufacturer of customized mechanical keyboards&keycaps. The keycap technologies include dyeing, Laser engraving, Hot sublimation and five-sided hot sublimation. The company is committed to e-commerce platform and international business cooperation, striving to provide customers with better products and services. The company's main business is mechanical keyboard&keycap&keycap puller&mechanical keyboard and peripheral equipment processing. It has a complete and scientific quality management system. The integrity, strength and product quality of Shenzhen Wuming Chengpin Technology Co., Ltd. are recognized by the industry. Now the company has 2 factories in Guangdong Shenzhen and Dongguan of China, with a total area of 4500 square metres. Welcome our friends to visit our factories, guide the company and business negotiation.
